title: Best of CCK: Real Names
description:
Almost all the guys at Barstool have nicknames, but none of the girls do. Dylan's family is trying to create some holiday magic. Zah and Kayce re-enact the Sopranos. Cheating allegations in trivia. Does the Mandalorian suck? Is Jetski a bro? The Barstool Lego kid is one step closer to a fulltime job.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
